creator: TRAINERIZE
descriptionHtml:
Forge is a national online personal training and wellness coaching company dedicated to the success of each and every one of our clients. We strive to provide the highest quality personal ﬁtness experience through communication, education and science based program design. Forge is ideal for people seeking clear communication with their personal trainer, exciting program design and constructive accountability to guide and accelerate their fitness journey. Every exercise, program outline and coaching session is focused on your needs and ability to deliver a world-class fitness experience!

Here are a 10 key benefits to working with Forge online:

1. Affordable access to a Personal Trainer who is completely focused on you.
2. No appointment to meet a trainer each day. Workout when you can.
3. Programs are created with your equipment or gym resources in mind.
4. Ideal for people who travel or just can’t get to the gym consistently.
5. Forge mobile app packed with helpful tools and communication portal.
6. Detailed result tracking and progress graphs built into the mobile app.
7. Exercise programs that are fresh and completely customized.
8. Video or phone calls with your trainer to fine-tune the program
9. Nutrition education designed especially for each client’s tastes and goals.
10. Access to Forge Fitness social media groups to build a resource community.

With the Forge Online Personal Training App, you can start tracking your workouts and meals, measuring results, and start achieving your fitness goals with your own affordable online personal trainer! Visit our website and enroll today: www.forgept.com

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Consistency is key with this release! Introducing habit streaks and achievement badges—a new way to motivate clients to build healthy habits! Clients can create habit winning streaks by completing a habit every day that it’s scheduled into their calendars. As their streak continues to grow, they'll unlock special achievement badges at various milestones. 

As always, we've also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
As much as we’d all like, big changes unfortunately don’t happen overnight. That’s why we’ve introduced habit coaching—a new way to help clients make small, sustainable lifestyle changes! Trainers can now create habits within our Master Habit Library and prescribe them to clients. As clients complete habits each day, they will earn habit streaks and unlock special achievement badges over time.
As always, we’ve also made some back-end upgrades and bug fixes to make your experience even better.
